buoyancy; நொய்ம்மை. (திவா.)  
2. thatwhich is easy to obtain or attain; எளிது.colloq  
3. that which is very small in quantity; அற்பம். (சீவக. 770.)  
4. (gram.) shortsignificant and very suggestive word  
as மன்  
